Package: statisticalRoughness
Title: Estimation of roughness exponents across scale for large areas
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Herv√©",
           family = "Guillon",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "herve@guillon.xyz",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package estimates the roughness exponent of the topography over a range of predefined spatial scales. It implements an efficient way of exploring the scaling of the topography for large areas by leveraging a tiling process. The spatial scales are defined using some factorization. 
